article.description: — Matt Knowling scored 26 points as Yale beat Eastern Washington 74-60 on Friday.
article.headline: Yale wins 74-60 against Eastern Washington
article.story: HONOLULU -- — Matt Knowling scored 26 points as Yale beat Eastern Washington 74-60 on Friday. Knowling added six rebounds for the Bulldogs (2-0). John Poulakidas shot 4 for 11, including 4 for 6 from beyond the arc to add 13 points. Isaiah Kelly went 4 of 6 from the field to finish with 11 points. Steele Venters led the way for the Eagles (0-2) with 15 points. Ethan Price added 14 points, six rebounds and three blocks for Eastern Washington. Casey Jones also had 11 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
